tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: I recently had a wisdom teeth extraction procedure done by Dr. Fahad and I am pleased with the level of care I received. From the initial consultation to the post-operative follow-up, Dr. Fahad and their team made me feel comfortable and well-informed throughout the entire process. During the procedure, Dr. Fahad was efficient and skilled, making the experience as painless as possible. I also found the clinic equipment and hygiene very well maintained. Dr. Fahad also took the time to explain the procedure and answer any questions I had, which helped me clear any concerns I had before the surgery. The recovery period was also relatively smooth, and I appreciated the clear and detailed instructions provided by him. Overall, I recommend the Dental Expertz clinic for anyone in need of wisdom teeth extraction. Their professionalism, expertise, and caring demeanor made what could have been a stressful experience a relatively easy one.
